Package: poly-tc8-profile-dev
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, openssh-server
Description: TC8 device profile: developer console
 Selects the developer role for the Polycom TC8: boots to a console with SSH and no kiosk lock (apply-config sets multi-user.target + tty1 autologin). Pulls openssh-server so remote access is always present. See polycom_dev/PROFILES-PLAN.md.
